import React from 'react'
import { Grid, Image,Card, Icon,Item, List  } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const GridExampleCelled = () => (
    <Grid celled>
      <Grid.Row>
        <Grid.Column width={3}>
        <Card>
            <Image src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/wireframe/image.png' wrapped ui={false} />
            <Card.Content>
                <Card.Header>TROPOLIS</Card.Header>
            </Card.Content>
            <Card.Content extra>
                <Icon name='map marker alternate' />Concho, Oregon
            </Card.Content>
        </Card>
        </Grid.Column>
        <Grid.Column width={13}>
            <List>
                <List.Item>
                    <List.Content>
                        <List.Header as='a' f>Fu Er Dai</List.Header>
                    </List.Content>
                </List.Item>
                <List.Item>
                    <List.Content>
                        <List.Description>QUORDATE</List.Description>
                        <List.Description>Rich</List.Description>
                        <List.Description>
                            Veniam laborum veniam commodo veniam nisi commodo. Culpa elit qui deserunt adipisicing ad dolor proident laboris adipisicing tempor eu. Elit do non occaecat exercitation ullamco deserunt. Aliquip labore consectetur elit id. Voluptate cupidatat dolore eiusmod labore eu. Consectetur ipsum mollit tempor eiusmod id ipsum sit.\r\n
                        </List.Description>
                        <List.Description>frankhorton@quordate.com</List.Description>
                        <List.Description>2020-02-11T04:48:37 -13:00</List.Description>
                    </List.Content>
                </List.Item>
            </List>
        </Grid.Column>
      </Grid.Row>
    </Grid>
  )
  
  export default GridExampleCelled
